data.description: Stunning 4-bed, 2-bath home with 1700 sq ft and a walk-out unfinished basement in a prime location. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious layout. Enjoy the convenience of a 2-car attached garage. Experience modern living with a Full Vivint Smart Home featuring surveillance, voice-controlled automation, smart dimmers, switches, and a smart irrigation system. The home is equipped with a Rain Soft smart water softener and triple reverse osmosis water filtration system for pristine water quality. This property seamlessly blends luxury, technology, and functionality for an unparalleled living experience.
